    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>像素风海洋生存模拟游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定价与后续更新说明</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏现已进入正式版本。我们仍计划在后续更新中持续加入新的系统与内容，进一步完善整体体验。随着内容规模与完成度的提升，未来价格可能会进行相应调整。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢在 EA 阶段支持我们的玩家。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创意工坊说明</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏已开启创意工坊，且游戏内置Mod接口，欢迎技术流玩家尝试Mod制作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/8c2b55a2625180c6776527af17acb9cb.webp?t=1768391709\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——洋流灾难，末日生存，作为幸存者想办法延续人类文明的火种</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——气候变幻，多种海洋季节复杂多变，灾害天气让人猝不及防</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——探索海洋，东西全靠捞，还可以奇遇获得物品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/2ee60b516df095940c08bbe79a47cbd9.poster.avif?t=1768391709\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/2ee60b516df095940c08bbe79a47cbd9.webm?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/2ee60b516df095940c08bbe79a47cbd9.mp4?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/a468ba0c3135aa9f5db47ec942c8f559.poster.avif?t=1768391709\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/a468ba0c3135aa9f5db47ec942c8f559.webm?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/a468ba0c3135aa9f5db47ec942c8f559.mp4?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/30ae7a5d334c9acfafeb2ac4f1a873e7.webp?t=1768391709\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——自由建造，打造海上移动生存基地，捕鱼、种植、烹饪，娱乐等样样齐全</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——计划生存，招募船员合理分工，抵御敌群以及洋流灾难，目的就是活下来</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/30303cbab7c876241f5ebd2042f6a23c.poster.avif?t=1768391709\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/30303cbab7c876241f5ebd2042f6a23c.webm?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/30303cbab7c876241f5ebd2042f6a23c.mp4?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/74cebec687c12020501630c42880085e.poster.avif?t=1768391709\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/74cebec687c12020501630c42880085e.webm?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/74cebec687c12020501630c42880085e.mp4?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/cc0128e688150c299b362ecd37ab9272.webp?t=1768391709\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——未知海怪、狂热份子、未知文明的突袭，让你一不小心就团灭</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——发展科技，技术迭代步入新文明，还能建造强大的防御武器系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/78170216980982cf8cfca011ee244f8e.poster.avif?t=1768391709\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/78170216980982cf8cfca011ee244f8e.webm?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/78170216980982cf8cfca011ee244f8e.mp4?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/6f9675625795d2eb0a62fda0ec29d949.poster.avif?t=1768391709\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/6f9675625795d2eb0a62fda0ec29d949.webm?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883840/extras/6f9675625795d2eb0a62fda0ec29d949.mp4?t=1768391709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
